#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:855
msgid ""
"<b>Enable dark theme:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the system theme is asked to use a darker styling for the "
"application <i>(i.e. dark UI elements on bright text)</i>.\n"
"\n"
"Note that not all system themes provide such a darker variant, therefore "
"enabling this setting might not have an effect."
msgstr ""
"<b>Washa mandhari meusi:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwashwa, mandhari ya mfumo yanaombwa kutumia mtindo mweusi zaidi kwa programu <i>(yaani vipengele vyeusi vya UI kwenye maandishi angavu)</i>.\n"
"\n"
"Kumbuka kuwa sio mandhari yote ya mfumo hutoa lahaja nyeusi zaidi, kwa hivyo kuwasha mpangilio huu kunaweza kusiwe na athari."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:873
msgid ""
"<b>Enable client-side decorations:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the search entry and main menu are displayed in the window title "
"bar.\n"
"\n"
"If disabled, the main menu is displayed as a menu bar with the search entry "
"below it.\n"
"This resembles a more traditional UI layout and takes a little bit more "
"space."
msgstr ""
"<b>Washa mapambo ya upande wa mteja:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwashwa, ingizo la utafutaji na menyu kuu huonyeshwa kwenye upau wa kichwa cha dirisha.\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwa imezimwa, menyu kuu itaonyeshwa kama upau wa menyu na ingizo la utafutaji chini yake.\n"
"Hii inafanana na mpangilio wa kawaida wa UI na inachukua nafasi kidogo zaidi."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:893
msgid ""
"<b>Use binary units instead of decimal units:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This settings controls how file sizes are displayed.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Binary units:</b> This refers to binary IEC prefixes <i>(e.g. 1 KiB = "
"1024 bytes)</i>\n"
"\t• <b>Decimal  units:</b> This refers to decimal SI prefixes <i>(e.g. 1 kB "
"= 1000 bytes)</i>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Tumia vitengo vya jozi badala ya vitengo vya desimali:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Mipangilio hii inadhibiti jinsi ukubwa wa faili unavyoonyeshwa.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Vizio-mbili:</b> Hii inarejelea viambishi awali vya IEC vya jozi <i>(k.m. 1 KiB = baiti 1024)</i>\n"
"\t• <b>Vizio vya decimal:</b> Hii inarejelea viambishi awali vya desimali vya SI <i>(k.m. 1 kB = baiti 1000)</i>"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:913
msgid ""
"<b>Remember window size:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the window size from the previous session will be restored when "
"you open an FSearch window.\n"
"\n"
"Note that some window managers ignore this request and force the window to "
"have a different size."
msgstr ""
"<b>Kumbuka ukubwa wa dirisha:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwashwa, saizi ya dirisha kutoka kwa kipindi cha awali itarejeshwa utakapofungua dirisha la FSearch.\n"
"\n"
"Kumbuka kuwa baadhi ya wasimamizi wa dirisha hupuuza ombi hili na kulazimisha dirisha kuwa na saizi tofauti."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:932
msgid ""
"<b>Behaviour after successfully opening a file:</b>\n"
"\n"
"When a file/folder was successfully opened one of the following actions can "
"be performed:\n"
"\t• <b>Nothing:</b> Nothing happens.\n"
"                        • <b>Minimize:</b> The currently selected FSearch "
"window becomes minimized.\n"
"\t• <b>Close:</b> Quit FSearch.\n"
"\n"
"You can configure if those actions should be triggered when the file was "
"opened with\n"
"\t• <b>keyboard shortcuts or menu entries</b> and/or\n"
"\t• <b>mouse click</b>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Tabia baada ya kufungua faili kwa ufanisi:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Wakati faili/folda ilifunguliwa kwa ufanisi moja ya vitendo vifuatavyo vinaweza kufanywa:\n"
"\t• <b>Hakuna:</b> Hakuna kinachotokea.\n"
"                        • <b>Punguza:</b> Dirisha la FSearch lililochaguliwa kwa sasa linapunguzwa.\n"
"\t• <b>Funga:</b> Acha FSearch.\n"
"\n"
"Unaweza kusanidi ikiwa vitendo hivyo vinapaswa kuanzishwa wakati faili ilifunguliwa na\n"
"\t• <b>njia za mkato za kibodi au maingizo ya menyu</b> na/au\n"
"\t• <b>bofya kipanya</b>"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:956
msgid ""
"<b>Show highlighted search terms:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the search terms will be highlighted in the results view. For "
"example when you search for \"foo\" all appearances of <i>foo</i> in file/"
"folder names will be highlighted with bold characters:\n"
"\n"
"\t<b>foo</b>bar.txt\n"
"\tfile.<b>foo</b>\n"
"\n"
"This also works for regular expressions and wildcard expressions starting or "
"ending with an asterisk. "
msgstr ""
"<b>Onyesha hoja za utafutaji zilizoangaziwa:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwashwa, hoja za utafutaji zitaangaziwa katika mwonekano wa matokeo. Kwa mfano unapotafuta \\\"foo\\\" mionekano yote ya <i>foo</i> katika majina ya faili/folda itaangaziwa kwa herufi nzito:\n"
"\n"
"\t<b>foo</b>bar.txt\n"
"\tfaili.<b>foo</b>\n"
"\n"
"Hii pia inafanya kazi kwa misemo ya kawaida na usemi wa kadi-mwitu kuanzia au kumalizia na nyota."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:978
msgid ""
"<b>Show tooltips:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the results view will show the full path of the focused file/"
"folder in a small tooltip window."
msgstr ""
"<b>Onyesha vidokezo vya zana:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwashwa, mwonekano wa matokeo utaonyesha njia kamili ya faili/folda iliyolengwa katika kidirisha kidogo cha kidokezo."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:995
msgid ""
"<b>Show icons in name column:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, file/folder icons will be shown in the name column."
msgstr ""
"<b>Onyesha aikoni katika safu wima ya jina:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwashwa, aikoni za faili/folda zitaonyeshwa kwenye safu wima ya jina."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1012
msgid ""
"<b>Remember column configuration:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the column configuration of the results view from the previous "
"session will be restored when you open an FSearch window. This includes the "
"size and visibility of all columns."
msgstr ""
"<b>Kumbuka usanidi wa safu wima:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwashwa, usanidi wa safu wima ya mwonekano wa matokeo kutoka kwa kipindi cha awali utarejeshwa utakapofungua dirisha la FSearch. Hii inajumuisha ukubwa na mwonekano wa safu wima zote."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1029
msgid ""
"<b>Remember sort order:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the sort order of the results view from the previous session "
"will be restored when you open an FSearch window."
msgstr ""
"<b>Kumbuka mpangilio wa kupanga:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwashwa, mpangilio wa mpangilio wa matokeo kutoka kwa kipindi kilichotangulia utarejeshwa utakapofungua dirisha la Utafutaji."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1046
msgid ""
"<b>Open path with double click in path column:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, double clicking in the path column will open the selected path."
msgstr ""
"<b>Fungua njia kwa kubofya mara mbili kwenye safu wima ya njia:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwashwa, kubofya mara mbili kwenye safu wima ya njia kutafungua njia iliyochaguliwa."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1063
msgid ""
"<b>Single click to open:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, a single click will open the selected file/folder. If you only "
"want to select a file/folder while this setting is active, you need to hold "
"<i>Ctrl</i> at the same time while clicking the file/folder."
msgstr ""
"<b>Mbofyo mmoja ili kufungua:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwashwa, kubofya mara moja kutafungua faili/folda iliyochaguliwa. Ikiwa unataka tu kuchagua faili/folda wakati mpangilio huu unatumika, unahitaji kushikilia <i>Ctrl</i> kwa wakati mmoja huku ukibofya faili/folda."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1080
msgid ""
"<b>Show database indexing status:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the path that is currently being indexed is displayed in the "
"statusbar."
msgstr ""
"<b>Onyesha hali ya kuorodhesha hifadhidata:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwashwa, njia ambayo inaorodheshwa kwa sasa inaonyeshwa kwenye upau wa hali."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1097
msgid ""
"<b>Show warning dialogs:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, a warning dialog is displayed when a file or folder failed to "
"open."
msgstr ""
"<b>Onyesha vidadisi vya onyo:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwashwa, kidirisha cha onyo huonyeshwa faili au folda iliposhindwa kufunguliwa."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1114
msgid ""
"<b>Search in path when query contains path separators:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, search terms containing path separators (i.e. \"/\") will be "
"automatically matched against the full path of a file or folder."
msgstr ""
"<b>Tafuta kwenye njia wakati hoja ina vitenganishi vya njia:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwashwa, maneno ya utafutaji yaliyo na vitenganishi vya njia (yaani \\\"/\\\") yatalinganishwa kiotomatiki dhidi ya njia kamili ya faili au folda."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1131
msgid ""
"<b>Match case when query contains at least one upper case character:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, search terms containing at least one upper case character will "
"trigger a case-sensitive search. This means a search term like <i>Foo</i> "
"will match <i>FooBar.txt</i> but not <i>foobar.txt</i>."
msgstr ""
"<b>Kesi inayolingana wakati hoja ina angalau herufi moja kubwa:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwezeshwa, hoja za utafutaji zilizo na angalau herufi moja kubwa zitaanzisha utafutaji nyeti sana. Hii inamaanisha kuwa neno la utafutaji kama <i>Foo</i> litalingana na <i>FooBar.txt</i> lakini si <i>foobar.txt</i>."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1148
msgid ""
"<b>Hide results when search is empty:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, no search results are displayed when the search entry is empty.\n"
"\n"
"If disabled, all files and folders will be displayed when the search entry "
"is empty."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ficha matokeo wakati utafutaji hauna:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwashwa, hakuna matokeo ya utafutaji yanayoonyeshwa wakati ingizo la utafutaji liko tupu.\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwa imezimwa, faili na folda zote zitaonyeshwa wakati ingizo la utafutaji litakuwa tupu."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1167
msgid ""
"<b>Search as you type:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the search is automatically updated with every keystroke.\n"
"\n"
"If disabled, the search is only updated when you hit <i>Enter</i> or press "
"the search button. "
msgstr ""
"<b>Tafuta unapoandika:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwashwa, utafutaji unasasishwa kiotomatiki kwa kila mibogoyo.\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwa imezimwa, utafutaji unasasishwa tu unapogonga <i>Enter</i> au bonyeza kitufe cha kutafuta."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1186
msgid ""
"<b>Update database on start:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the database will be updated automatically in the background "
"when you start FSearch."
msgstr ""
"<b>Sasisha hifadhidata unapoanza:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwashwa, hifadhidata itasasishwa kiotomatiki chinichini unapoanzisha Utafutaji wa FSearch."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1203
msgid ""
"<b>Included folders:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This list contains all folders you want to include in the database.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Active:</b> If enabled, the path will included in the database to be "
"searched in.\n"
"\t• <b>Path:</b> The full path to be included.\n"
"\t• <b>One Filesystem:</b> If enabled, FSearch won't cross filesystem "
"boundaries for this folder"
msgstr ""
"<b>Folda zilizojumuishwa:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Orodha hii ina folda zote unazotaka kujumuisha kwenye hifadhidata.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Inatumika:</b> Ikiwashwa, njia itajumuishwa kwenye hifadhidata itakayotafutwa.\n"
"\t• <b>Njia:</b> Njia kamili ya kujumuishwa.\n"
"\t• <b>Mfumo Mmoja wa Faili:</b> Ikiwashwa, FSearch haitavuka mipaka ya mfumo wa faili kwa folda hii."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1224
msgid ""
"<b>Add folder to database:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button opens a dialog where you can select a folder you want to include "
"in the database for searching."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ongeza folda kwenye hifadhidata:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Kitufe hiki hufungua mazungumzo ambapo unaweza kuchagua folda unayotaka kujumuisha kwenye hifadhidata kwa ajili ya kutafuta."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1241
msgid ""
"<b>Add a specific path:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Type the full path of a folder here and click the button next to it to "
"include that folder in the database. This is useful for adding a path "
"directly without browsing for it."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ongeza njia mahususi:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Andika njia kamili ya folda hapa na ubofye kitufe kilicho karibu nayo ili kujumuisha folda hiyo kwenye hifadhidata. Hii ni muhimu kwa kuongeza njia moja kwa moja bila kuvinjari kwa hiyo."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1258
msgid ""
"<b>Remove selected row:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This removes the selected folder from the list of included folders."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ondoa safu mlalo iliyochaguliwa:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Hii huondoa folda iliyochaguliwa kutoka kwa orodha ya folda zilizojumuishwa."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1275
msgid ""
"<b>Attempt to monitor:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, FSearch watches this folder for changes and keeps the database "
"up to date automatically, so you don't have to rescan manually.\n"
"\n"
"Monitoring isn't supported on every file system and uses a small amount of "
"system resources per watched folder. For large directory trees with many "
"files the system may run out of resources to watch them all."
msgstr ""
"<b>Jaribio la kufuatilia:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwashwa, FSearch hutazama folda hii kwa mabadiliko na husasisha hifadhidata kiotomatiki, kwa hivyo huhitaji kuchanganua tena wewe mwenyewe.\n"
"\n"
"Ufuatiliaji hautumiki kwenye kila mfumo wa faili na hutumia kiasi kidogo cha rasilimali za mfumo kwa kila folda inayotazamwa. Kwa miti mikubwa ya saraka iliyo na faili nyingi mfumo unaweza kukosa rasilimali za kuzitazama zote."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1294
msgid ""
"<b>Scan after launch:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, this folder is rescanned every time FSearch starts, so the "
"database reflects any changes made while FSearch wasn't running."
msgstr ""
"<b>Changanua baada ya uzinduzi:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwashwa, folda hii huchanganuliwa upya kila mara FSearch inapoanza, kwa hivyo hifadhidata huakisi mabadiliko yoyote yaliyofanywa wakati FSearch haikufanya kazi."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1311
msgid ""
"<b>Stay on one file system:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, FSearch won't cross file system boundaries while scanning this "
"folder. Mounted file systems below it (e.g. external drives or network "
"shares) are skipped."
msgstr ""
"<b>Kaa kwenye mfumo mmoja wa faili:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwashwa, FSearch haitavuka mipaka ya mfumo wa faili wakati wa kuchanganua folda hii. Mifumo ya faili iliyowekwa chini yake (k.m. hifadhi za nje au ushiriki wa mtandao) imerukwa."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1328
msgid ""
"<b>Rescan every:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, this folder is rescanned automatically at the given interval. "
"Use the hours and minutes fields to set how often the rescan happens.\n"
"\n"
"This is useful for folders on file systems that can't be monitored for "
"changes."
msgstr ""
"<b>Changanua upya kila:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwashwa, folda hii inachanganuliwa upya kiotomatiki kwa muda uliotolewa. Tumia sehemu za saa na dakika kuweka ni mara ngapi kuchanganua hufanyika.\n"
"\n"
"Hii ni muhimu kwa folda kwenye mifumo ya faili ambayo haiwezi kufuatiliwa kwa mabadiliko."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1347
msgid ""
"<b>Exclude rules:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This list contains rules for the files and folders you want to exclude from "
"the database.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Active:</b> If enabled, the rule is applied and matching items are "
"excluded.\n"
"\t• <b>Pattern:</b> The text matched against each item, interpreted "
"according to the Type.\n"
"\t• <b>Type:</b> How the pattern is interpreted — <i>Literal</i> (exact "
"text), <i>Wildcard</i> (using * and ?) or <i>Regex</i> (a regular "
"expression).\n"
"\t• <b>Match:</b> Whether the pattern is matched against the item's <i>Full "
"Path</i> or only its <i>Basename</i> (the name without the path).\n"
"\t• <b>Applies To:</b> Whether the rule affects <i>Files</i>, <i>Folders</i> "
"or both."
msgstr ""
"<b>Toa sheria:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Orodha hii ina sheria za faili na folda unazotaka kuziondoa kwenye hifadhidata.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Inatumika:</b> Ikiwashwa, sheria itatumika na vipengee vinavyolingana havijajumuishwa.\n"
"\t• <b>Muundo:</b> Maandishi yanalingana dhidi ya kila kipengee, yamefasiriwa kulingana na Aina.\n"
"\t• <b>Aina:</b> Jinsi mchoro unavyofasiriwa — <i>Literal</i> (maandishi kamili), <i>Wildcard</i> (kwa kutumia * na ?) au <i>Regex</i> (maneno ya kawaida).\n"
"\t• <b>Inalingana:</b> Iwapo mchoro unalingana na <i>Njia Kamili</i> ya bidhaa au <i>Jina lake la Msingi pekee</i> (jina lisilo na njia).\n"
"\t• <b>Inatumika Kwa:</b> Iwapo sheria inaathiri <i>Faili</i>, <i>Folda</i> au zote mbili."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1370
msgid ""
"<b>Add exclude rule:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This adds a new, empty rule to the list. Edit its Pattern, Type, Match and "
"Applies To columns to control what gets excluded from the database."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ongeza kutenga sheria:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Hii inaongeza sheria mpya, tupu kwenye orodha. Hariri Mchoro wake, Aina, Mechi na Hutumika kwa safu wima ili kudhibiti kile ambacho hakijumuishwi kwenye hifadhidata."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1387
msgid ""
"<b>Remove selected row:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This removes the selected rule from the list of exclude rules."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ondoa safu mlalo iliyochaguliwa:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Hii huondoa sheria iliyochaguliwa kutoka kwa orodha ya kutojumuisha sheria."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1404
msgid ""
"<b>Restore default exclude rules:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button restores the default set of exclude rules.\n"
"\n"
"⚠ All rules which were created or edited by the user will be lost! ⚠"
msgstr ""
"<b>Rejesha chaguomsingi tenga sheria:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Kitufe hiki kinarejesha seti chaguo-msingi ya kutojumuisha sheria.\n"
"\n"
"⚠ Sheria zote ambazo ziliundwa au kuhaririwa na mtumiaji zitapotea! ⚠"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1423
msgid ""
"<b>Exclude files and folders from database:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This is a semi-colon separated list of files (or folders) you want to "
"exclude from the database. For example <i>.git;.cache;*.swp</i> will exclude "
"all files or folders which are called either <i>.git</i> or <i>.cache</i> or "
"end with <i>.swp</i>."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ondoa faili na folda kutoka kwa hifadhidata:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Hii ni orodha iliyotenganishwa ya nusu koloni ya faili (au folda) unazotaka kuziondoa kwenye hifadhidata. Kwa mfano <i>.git;.cache;*.swp</i> haitajumuisha faili au folda zote zinazoitwa ama <i>.git</i> au <i>.cache</i> au kuishia na <i>.swp</i>."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1440
msgid ""
"<b>Exclude hidden files and folders:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, hidden files and folders will be excluded from the database "
"<i>(i.e. all files or folders which start with a dot character)</i>."
msgstr ""
"<b>Tenga faili na folda zilizofichwa:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwashwa, faili na folda zilizofichwa zitatengwa kwenye hifadhidata <i>(yaani faili zote au folda zinazoanza na herufi ya nukta)</i>."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1457
msgid "Focus a setting to get a detailed description of what it does."
msgstr "Lenga mpangilio ili kupata maelezo ya kina ya kile kinachofanya."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1470
msgid ""
"<b>Periodically update database at a specific time interval:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled and as long as FSearch is running, the database will be updated "
"periodically with the given time interval.\n"
"\n"
"If you want to update the database in the background, even when FSearch is "
"not running, you should use tools like cron or systemd timers to "
"periodically trigger the update with:\n"
"\n"
"<i><tt>fsearch --update-database</tt></i>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Sasisha hifadhidata mara kwa mara kwa muda maalum:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwashwa na mradi FSearch inaendeshwa, hifadhidata itasasishwa mara kwa mara kwa muda uliotolewa.\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwa unataka kusasisha hifadhidata chinichini, hata wakati FSearch haifanyiki, unapaswa kutumia zana kama cron au vipima saa vya mfumo ili kuanzisha sasisho mara kwa mara na:\n"
"\n"
"<i><tt>fsearch --update-database</tt></i>"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1491
msgid ""
"<b>Launch desktop files:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, activating a <i>.desktop</i> file will launch the application "
"defined within that file. This way FSearch can act like an application "
"launcher. Otherwise the <i>.desktop</i> file will be opened with the default "
"handler for this type of files, which is usually a text editor."
msgstr ""
"<b>Zindua faili za eneo-kazi:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwashwa, kuwezesha faili ya <i>.desktop</i> kutazindua programu iliyofafanuliwa ndani ya faili hiyo. Kwa njia hii FSearch inaweza kutenda kama kizindua programu. Vinginevyo faili ya <i>.desktop</i> itafunguliwa kwa kidhibiti chaguo-msingi cha aina hii ya faili, ambayo kwa kawaida ni kihariri cha maandishi."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1508
msgid ""
"<b>Filters:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This is a list of all available filters. A filter is a predefined search.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Name:</b> A unique and descriptive identifier for the filter\n"
"\t• <b>Macro:</b> By typing the macro text followed by a ':' you can enable "
"the filter on demand\n"
"\t• <b>Query:</b> The search term by which the database should be filtered"
msgstr ""
"<b>Vichujio:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Hii ni orodha ya vichujio vyote vinavyopatikana. Kichujio ni utafutaji uliofafanuliwa awali.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Jina:</b> Kitambulishi cha kipekee na cha maelezo kwa kichujio\n"
"\t• <b>Makro:</b> Kwa kuandika maandishi makubwa yakifuatiwa na ':' unaweza kuwezesha kichujio unapohitaji.\n"
"\t• <b>Hoja:</b> Neno la utafutaji ambalo hifadhidata inapaswa kuchujwa"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1529
msgid ""
"<b>Add a new filter:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button opens a dialog where you can edit a new filter."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ongeza kichujio kipya:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Kitufe hiki hufungua kidirisha ambapo unaweza kuhariri kichujio kipya."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1546
msgid ""
"<b>Remove selected filter:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button removes the currently selected filter."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ondoa kichujio ulichochagua:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Kitufe hiki huondoa kichujio kilichochaguliwa kwa sasa."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1563
msgid ""
"<b>Edit selected filter:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button opens a dialog where you can edit the selected filter."
msgstr ""
"<b>Hariri kichujio kilichochaguliwa:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Kitufe hiki hufungua kidirisha ambapo unaweza kuhariri kichujio kilichochaguliwa."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1580
msgid ""
"<b>Restore default filters:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button restores the default filter configuration.\n"
"\n"
"⚠ All filters which were created or edited by the user will be lost! ⚠"
msgstr ""
"<b>Rejesha vichujio chaguomsingi:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Kitufe hiki kinarejesha usanidi chaguo-msingi wa kichujio.\n"
"\n"
"⚠ Vichungi vyote vilivyoundwa au kuhaririwa na mtumiaji vitapotea! ⚠"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1599
msgid ""
"<b>Exit on Escape:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, FSearch exits when the Escape key is pressed instead of the "
"window being minimized."
msgstr ""
"<b>Toka kwenye Escape:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwashwa, Utafutaji wa FSearch huondoka wakati kitufe cha Escape kimebonyezwa badala ya dirisha kupunguzwa."

